712129f-a.text:

from the Third Avenue 'E1'' atation. At the left is the

towers the 7lst Regiment Armory and the Vanderbilt Hotel.
Note the absence of the Empire State Building. In thw
center is the Cameron Bldg. outlined against the mcrble
B. Altmen \& Co. store. To the right are the two Park
Avenue apartments at 35th Street. The castleatted tower
above, is atop the Combustion Engineering Bldg.
